{"tid":1461352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"真心想放棄","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:10:51.000Z","uid":268976,"like":10,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"312b41a153afdf54452d5c15652a67727c6880a4","tid":1461352,"uid":268976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"香港人善忘到一個地步令我懷疑其實香港人有幾想贏。<br />\n<br />\n受傷既，被捕既，全部被拋諸腦後。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求我唔要喇，求下香港人去救反被捕既人啦，真係好簡單架咋，至要你地肯出現就可以喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我勇武既做過，街站文宣都做過，到琴晚留守係機場，得幾十人都繼續留，係咁有人話禁區點點點，班狗點點點，話好危險，最後當然無事，我地無嬲過所有5點6點或者反左機場再走過既人，因為白色恐怖，令好多人卻步。<br />\n<br />\n但我地凌晨四點嘅時候有班唔甘心，好想贏，對香港人有信心既連登仔女，傾左3個幾鐘，想開一個POST去停止對運動不利既風向，開左一個Post, 希望朝早同下就可以見到大家再返反機場，齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n宜家，人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">若果香港人金魚腦到只有一日記憶，一晚既憤怒，咁仲要有幾多位手足自殺，有幾多隻眼比子彈射中，先到勝利既一刻？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">說好的煲底再會呢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"6ee25a3754be589c0b9967c14fa5b5a9787edc4f","tid":1461352,"uid":268976,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"人呢，去曬邊到？"},{"pid":"5d923ce6a01bd6a0ef61c46ccd6d150220ff2f73","tid":1461352,"uid":268976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"仲要有幾多個手足犧牲"},{"pid":"978d83ccdcc34dcb598ff3e83fe1ffc84adc9c4c","tid":1461352,"uid":268976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"人呢？"},{"pid":"904b91dfffcd0282c6d1f3895bb386ba3f30ca15","tid":1461352,"uid":107596,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"出去 唔好涼冷氣<br />\n我放工到"},{"pid":"bda6252427ac73b277498b1d0357266c5c6b0084","tid":1461352,"uid":268976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:27:23.000Z","msg":"肯出現就可以喇"},{"pid":"24f5051805732893c573a0fe7ee505f04e8e22c6","tid":1461352,"uid":74432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a757e14555d966c46e0fea5173f21c23265f93e5","tid":1461352,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"[置頂] [上線啦!!!] 夢遊機場 Online攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDeeMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDeeMS</a>"},{"pid":"6de8128371500abaa88ebe953f8c383f0be4051e","tid":1461352,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:30.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46383a9524930d15c6b07d2818ee83f7cff44eb0","tid":1461352,"uid":33651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"連狗幾時限P牌出帖"},{"pid":"cd6e91ba2f8c18838d4134e003ed8fddec796ac2","tid":1461352,"uid":98139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"冇哂人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e607e09d76e0cf0e18b1c7d5773170bd1413733","tid":1461352,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"出黎啊自由西"},{"pid":"da24ad2e066f852692129e6e8ccdaf3eeace47d7","tid":1461352,"uid":272900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"冷靜，好多人唔可以每日罷工<br />\n收工會出，唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14825a1b2aafda210660c1ab518007d3a18c9889","tid":1461352,"uid":273747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"唔係日日都可以請假嫁...<br />\n收工就來啦."},{"pid":"f42e9ee348030a8f4820dbfbd43578bc006d0ea9","tid":1461352,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904b91dfffcd0282c6d1f3895bb386ba3f30ca15","tid":1461352,"uid":107596,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"出去 唔好涼冷氣<br />\n我放工到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"可以涼,入機場涼"},{"pid":"0f9296e13cd4b30f2708e2157544e52cd67902eb","tid":1461352,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6829f3e599947ae2bb49cc138b770786e467c5ec","tid":1461352,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"應承你 收工來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e462bd7600e5772e64f6feccd60b986eaf39c7","tid":1461352,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fbc9601c996d8dae0de8a3944d5811aad949df3","tid":1461352,"uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"呢個post睇到返工對香港人係最重要"},{"pid":"bb85fe8ffee7c5a94937c28a2b4dfe70d03b7dce","tid":1461352,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"機場嘅人全部上離境大堂南北面<br />\n呢度根本唔夠人封曬<br />\n得一千人左右<br />\n但勁多人係樓下好安逸咁坐緊<br />\n我落去講 <br />\n竟然俾人話我係黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔明發生緊咩事<br />\n我唔係叫人返屋企<br />\n我地係上面封得咁辛苦<br />\n你地有一班人係下面坐下食下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真 今日唔成功 <br />\n絕對係因為大家唔信隊友所致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0632cad703bca9a3a635d0320465395d13a00a1","tid":1461352,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"沉默，是最大的幫兇，也是最大的暴力。<br />\n<br />\n當社會面對各種民生問題，醫療問題、市民上車無望、自殺問題、產業單一化、生活成本高昂、國際競爭力不斷下滑... ...我們的政府正在做什麼？推行國民教育、建高鐵、建港珠澳大橋、研究去除通識科、推動明日大嶼、修訂逃犯條例，這些政策計劃真的有助改善民生嗎？<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例，一百萬人上街，政府仍打算強推二讀，兩個多月來的抗爭，爭取自由、民主的和平示威者變成暴徒，警察濫暴，以各種威迫手段迫使市民噤聲，當人民選擇沉默，換來的卻是當權者的得寸進尺，我們還可以相信我們的法制嗎？還能相信當權者嗎？<br />\n<br />\n721是香港黑暗的一天，當生活於亞洲最安全城巿的居民，乘坐大型交通工具回家時，竟然可以於鬧市中被有組織人士襲擊，香港人的公僕竟然可以視若無睹，香港作為一個無槍城市，擁有最強武力的執法者，竟然可以以不安全為由而關上大閘，那手無寸鐵的普羅大眾，應如何是好？往後我們還能告訴別人香港是一個安全城市嗎？<br />\n<br />\n當警隊堅持聲稱自己公平執法同時，為何過往發生黑幫斬人案，警方會馬上高姿態掃蕩黑幫，反觀是次事件，警方採取了什麼行動？當黑幫招搖過市時，大街小巷的閉路電視總能拍攝到白衣暴徒吧？然後被捕人士無一被起訴<br />\n<br />\n事件過後，一班政棍竟妄想把元朗無差別打人事件與示威者混為一談，將示威者與暴力掛勾，混淆視聽，當人民選擇沉默的同時，面對的卻是當權者步步進逼，除了走上街頭，手無寸鐵的市民還能用什麼方式表達不滿？<br />\n<br />\n當你天真的以為他們會悔過時，別忘了還有8.11&mdash;更黑暗的一天<br />\n<br />\n當管治者不斷破壞我們的核心價值，新聞自由、集會自由、言論自由不斷被扼殺，我們的法制、人權受到破壞，誠信、廉潔蕩然無存的情況下，當面對欺壓，我們選擇視若無睹，當我們選擇繼續沉默，香港的核心價值將在無聲中死去。你願意站岀來為自己、為下一代爭取更好的香港嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班連登傻仔，入乜撚嘢機場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"711d4c32c6698f873ca3962678ed6421e7f39a1d","tid":1461352,"uid":214177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n琴晚一個人坐埋一邊開post叫人再入機場<br />\n推唔起post 留唔住人<br />\n早走唔緊要<br />\n最緊要係要再返黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d59853d039f6ac7c724379892c43c745b9c5451","tid":1461352,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fbc9601c996d8dae0de8a3944d5811aad949df3","tid":1461352,"uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"呢個post睇到返工對香港人係最重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"所以罷工冇咩可能做到"},{"pid":"ef335887fc774a73ade9ef48228e629b761ab25c","tid":1461352,"uid":209795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，分化撚"},{"pid":"9c01bf6bbd7d07cb313d8c73dbfb471135b126b7","tid":1461352,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"又話還眼，<span style=\"color: red;\">眼球都未有一隻就走</span>，得把口<br />\n<br />\n解散軍仲要鬧返留守嘅人轉頭，<span style=\"color: red;\">用「好擔心你哋」「已經贏咗」趕走後援、孤立前線</span><br />\n<br />\n好想由得香港人承受自己嘅選擇，<span style=\"color: red;\">為佢哋傷亡一啲都唔值得</span>"}]}